Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.23,0:21:29.82,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}自由所剩无几
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.54,0:21:49.13,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}是时候上阵了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.17,0:21:51.34,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不知何为失败
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.47,0:21:54.09,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}却寻得些线索
